function Home() { return (//Main page text

What is Dungeons and Dragons

Dungeons and Dragons(D&D) is a tabletop roleplaying game that allows you to play as a fantasy character in a wide variety of fantasy settings.



What this app does

This app allows you to store the basic information that builds up the framework of your character

What information can I store on this app?

You can store the following information:

1. Your characters name

2. Your characters looks with the use of an image url link

3. Your characters race(human, elf, dward, ect)

4. Your characters Main(fighter, rouge, wizard, ect) and subclass(Champion, Assassin, Necromancer)

); } export default Home;
